Lots of English words are just the same in French at least I know miaw is , and croquet , and fiance . 
Oh , pussies , do be quiet ! Let's stroke them as hard as we can with both hands , and perhaps they'll stop . 
Anthea had always been afraid of cows but now she tried to be brave . 
'Anyway , it can't run after me , she said to herself 'There isn't room for it even to begin to run . 
The cow was perfectly placid . 
She behaved like a strayed duchess till some one brought a saucer for the milk , and some one else tried to milk the cow into it . 
You may think it is easy , but it is not . 
All the children were by this time strung up to a pitch of heroism that would have been impossible to them in their ordinary condition . 
Anthea , holding the saucer , now advanced towards the cow . 
She remembered to have heard that cows , when milked by strangers , are susceptible to the soothing influence of the human voice . 
So , clutching her saucer very tight , she sought for words to whose soothing influence the cow might be susceptible . 
Lie down , then , good dog , lie down ! was all that she could think of to say , and she said it . 
The situation , full of grey mewing cats , was too serious for that . 
Then Anthea , with a beating heart , tried to milk the cow . 
'Oh , how much too horrid everything is ! she cried . 
Let's go to bed and leave the horrid cats with the hateful cow . 
Perhaps somebody will eat somebody else . 
'It is most truly awful , said Anthea , 'and I am so tired . 
Let's let the cats loose . 
'And the cow , perhaps ? said Cyril . 
'The police would find us at once . 
That cow would stand at the gate and mew I mean moo to come in . 
And so would the cats . 
