ISN'T it good and kind of him ? She winked at the others , and though they did not understand they played up loyally . 
'How do ? said Cyril , 'Very glad to meet you . 
Don't let us interrupt the milking . 
'I shall 'ave a 'ead and a 'arf in the morning , and no bloomin' error , remarked the burglar but he began to milk the cow . 
Not the same one a much stronger sort . 
He thought it really was a foundling orphan we'd got . 
He pranced off when he'd got the cat bags off his face thought we'd bolted . 
The gentle samishness of the milk swishing into the hand bowl seemed to have soothed the burglar very much . 
Finding him in this softened mood , Jane said 'I wish you'd tell us how you came to choose our house for your burglaring to night . 
I am awfully glad you did . 
You have been so kind . 
I don't know what we should have done without you , she added hastily . 
'We all love you ever so . 
And I don't know but what it won't be my last . 
For this 'ere cow , she reminds me of my father , and I know 'ow 'e'd 'ave 'ided me if I'd laid 'ands on a 'a'penny as wasn't my own . 
